raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Naomi: Hey! 
Naomi: Morning!
Naomi: img: naomi/11
Player: Morning
Naomi: Good work out there with Caleb!
Naomi: I just got your application put together and everything looks good!
Player: Awesome
Naomi: Of course I can't comment on the pictures 😁
Naomi: Buuut...
Naomi: 😉😉👍
Player: Haha thanks!
Player: What about Mabel's application?
if Story.mabel_desire > 0:
	Naomi: I can't comment on that either... but
	Naomi: 😳😍🥵🍑
	Player: 😳
	Player: Interesting, I wonder if there's something I should know 😁
	Naomi: I wonder too 🤭
	Naomi: Feel free to ask her
else:
	Naomi: I can't comment on that either... but
	Naomi: 😂😊🥰
	Player: Sounds like she enjoyed it
	Naomi: Sounds like she did
Naomi: I seriously wish I could adopt her as my sister or something 🥰
Naomi: I don't get along with mine
Naomi: Anyway, I don't want to bother you with that!
Player: No bother!
Naomi: You and Mabel will get your official invites on Saturday! 🥳
Player: Glad to hear it!
Naomi: You'll be invited to our little community group and we'll start discussing club activities and tasks together
Player: Thanks, looking forward to it!
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
